OL,3,CFour people 'critically injured' after
OL,4,Ctwo trains crash head-on in Denmark
OL,6,FMultiple people have been injured
OL,7,Fafter two trains crashed into each
OL,8,Fother in Denmark.
OL,10,FThe two trains collided head-on around
OL,11,F6.30am just north of Hillerod, North
OL,12,FZealand, about 25 miles above
OL,13,FCopenhagen, on a line linking the
OL,14,Ftowns of Hillerod and Kagerup.
OL,16,FPolice have said there are at least
OL,17,Ffive to ten people injured, according
OL,18,Fto Danish public broadcaster DR.
OL,20,FAt least four are in a critical
OL,21,Fcondition, DR reports.
OL,26,@sD@\o|vD@Qo|
