OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776960675
OL,3,CFour people 'critically injured' after
OL,4,Ctwo trains crash head-on in Denmark
OL,6,FThe incident prompted a huge emergency
OL,7,Fresponse for what police called a
OL,8,Fmajor accident.
OL,10,FInjured people have been transported
OL,11,Ffrom the scene by helicopter and
OL,12,Fambulance, the Greater Copenhagen Fire
OL,13,FDepartment said on X.
OL,15,F"I am deeply shaken and shocked and my
OL,16,Fthoughts are with all those involved,"
OL,17,FTrine Egetved, the mayor of Gribskov
OL,18,FMunicipality - an area just north of
OL,19,Fthe accident - wrote in a post on
OL,20,FFacebook.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
