OL,3,CFour people 'critically injured' after
OL,4,Ctwo trains crash head-on in Denmark
OL,6,F"The local track is used by many
OL,7,FGribskov citizens, employees and
OL,8,Fpupils.
OL,10,F"Emergency services are working at
OL,11,Ffull pressure, and we are trying from
OL,12,Fthe central team to get an overview of
OL,13,Fwhat has happened more accurately and
OL,14,Fmake sure that everyone gets the help
OL,15,Fthey need."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
